{"tid":1474461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後逢週末先去機場參觀其實可唔可行？","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:11:47.000Z","uid":295353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d10a5703f8ae6af01cc41e5727344747cfeb7111","tid":1474461,"uid":295353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"P牌絲第一次認真開post，請各位巴絲前輩屌得細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到8月13號嘅第二次接機送機活動比8月12號嗰日少咁多人，因為係好多人12號嗰日特登請一日假去參與，而要求打工仔連續請兩日假都唔容易。 我就諗如果我哋集氣嚟多一次/多幾次大規模啲嘅接機送機活動，仲要限定星期六日，趁啲人唔使返工唔使請假就會多啲人出嚟，有冇可能會比12號嗰一次更加成功？最重要嘅係要夠時間集中火力文宣，同埋時間日期方面要就翻要返工嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋既然佢而家唔俾由正門入機場，咁咪全世界一齊搭機鐵入去囉，有車嘅揸車出嚟去接機送機都得，分分鐘更加容易做到熱鬧嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06a9b7583ee82cabf463c101b44191f47e2a27e","tid":1474461,"uid":295353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"818大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c52b27a937a846e299d58e0039c2b81690f336","tid":1474461,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:07:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻<br />\n<br />\n機場新戰線活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Jd1WPw6gMNjry1PQ1RXB8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJd1WPw6gMNjry1PQ1RXB8g&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=2f3a9299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Jd1WPw6gMNjry1PQ1RXB8g</a>"},{"pid":"47b468ce7b0dfa5e1f35881eb1685704078dc1f1","tid":1474461,"uid":295353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c52b27a937a846e299d58e0039c2b81690f336","tid":1474461,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:07:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻<br />\n<br />\n機場新戰線活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Jd1WPw6gMNjry1PQ1RXB8g\" data-sr-url=\"h